e modifications to the theory of Kuranishi\nspaces, the latter will allow us to construct a virtual fundamental class for\nevery such log moduli space and define relative GW invariants without any\nrestriction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Sep 2017 16:59:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Oct 2019 14:02:13 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 17 Jul 2020 15:13:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-17"}
